WEBVTT

00:04.270 --> 00:06.500
Hello. Hi.

00:07.240 --> 00:11.040
My name is Leslie Knope, and I work for
the Parks and Recreation Department.

00:11.111 --> 00:13.341
Can I ask you
a few questions?

00:14.381 --> 00:16.076
Would you say
that you are,

00:16.149 --> 00:18.310
"Enjoying yourself
and having fun,

00:18.385 --> 00:20.250
"having a moderate
amount of fun

00:20.320 --> 00:21.753
"and somewhat
enjoying yourself,

00:21.821 --> 00:24.517
"or having no fun
and no enjoyment?"

00:25.992 --> 00:27.789
I'm gonna put
a lot of fun.

00:27.861 --> 00:31.058
Ms. Knope,
there's a drunk stuck in the slide.

00:31.631 --> 00:33.292
Sir, this is
a children's slide.

00:33.366 --> 00:35.129
- You're not allowed to sleep in here.
- What is?

00:35.201 --> 00:36.225
<i>You know,</i>
<i>when I first tell people</i>

00:36.302 --> 00:37.428
<i>that I work in the government,</i>
<i>they say,</i>

00:37.504 --> 00:39.335
"Oh. The government.
The government stinks.

00:39.406 --> 00:41.533
"The lines are too long
at the DMV."

00:41.608 --> 00:43.235
<i>But now things</i>
<i>have changed.</i>

00:43.309 --> 00:44.970
<i>People need our help.</i>

00:45.045 --> 00:47.343
And it feels good
to be needed.

00:47.414 --> 00:48.676
Could you put
your arms to your side?

00:48.748 --> 00:49.737
Wait...

00:49.816 --> 00:51.181
And that might help you
slide down a little easier.

00:51.251 --> 00:52.582
We don't...
Do you want to come this way?

00:52.652 --> 00:54.085
Uh-uh.
Okay, we're gonna need you to get out.

00:54.154 --> 00:55.246
Can you
please go away?

00:55.321 --> 00:56.345
Get out of the slide.
Okay?

00:56.423 --> 00:58.118
You're... Can you please go away?
Here we go!

00:58.191 --> 01:00.352
Okay, wake up. Here we go.
Out of the slide.

01:00.427 --> 01:02.895
<i>You know, government</i>
<i>isn't just a boys' club anymore.</i>

01:02.962 --> 01:07.956
Women are everywhere. It's a great
time to be a woman in politics.

01:08.034 --> 01:11.834
<i>Hillary Clinton,</i>
<i>Sarah Palin, me, Nancy Pelosi.</i>

01:12.172 --> 01:13.503
We did it!

01:13.873 --> 01:15.670
<i>You know, I like to</i>
<i>tell people, you know,</i>

01:15.742 --> 01:17.471
<i>"Get on board</i>
<i>and buckle up,</i>

01:17.544 --> 01:19.876
<i>"because my ride's</i>
<i>gonna be a big one."</i>

01:19.946 --> 01:21.573
<i>And if you get motion sickness,</i>
<i>you know,</i>

01:21.648 --> 01:23.206
<i>put your head</i>
<i>between your knees</i>

01:23.283 --> 01:26.150
'cause Leslie Knope's
stopping for no one.

